query:
INSERT INTO PointDistributionData (
           filter_id,
           is_pro_leaderboard,
           a,
           b,
           loc,
           scale,
           top_scale
         )
         VALUES
           (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?),
           (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
         ON DUPLICATE KEY
         UPDATE a = VALUES(a),
                b = VALUES(b),
                loc = VALUES(loc),
                scale = VALUES(loc),
                top_scale = VALUES(top_scale)
